data.description: Fantastic 2,706 sq ft home in Cedar Home Square, 5 bedroom 2.75 bathroom. Enjoy the extra space with a bonus room and great room with gas fireplace to cozy up next to on cold nights. Beautiful open kitchen with quartz countertops, large island, SS sink and appliances with gas range. Large primary bedroom with 5 piece en suite bath featuring corner soaking tub and large walk-in closet. Three car garage includes plenty of storage space. Fenced in backyard with decoratively paved gazebo, sunken firepit and covered hot tub with water feature for entertaining. Safe quiet neighborhood, close to shopping and restaurants, minimal traffic for walking and biking. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
